#13001
The Eastern Plains~
You look down at the ground beneath your feet as you quickly move through the
plains, not wanting to be here a minute longer than necessary.  Luckily you
look up just as you come to a rather large tree.  Somehow in the middle of
nowhere this tree seems to be surviving, despite what years of cold and harsh
weather and the absence of any water for miles.  Many questions run through
your mind on this peculiar occurrence, and what odd fate may have led you to
it.  You study it over, and see many long, strong branches leading up to the
top hidden in the green leafage.
~
