An Underground stream~
You fall through the middle of the tree, and hit the ground with much
tumultuousness.  You straighten yourself, stand up, gather your bearings, and
look at what is an underground stream flowing north.  Now you realize how the
tree is living, but to why it was hollowed out you have yet to discover.  You
also look upwards, this place is pretty dark, except for what light can enter
in through the hole from which you entered.  It's pretty far up there, maybe if
you had wings or something you could fly up there...
